### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AI-MSHM  –  Onboarding Endpoints
###  Base prefix: /api/v1/onboarding/
###
###  Flow:  step/1 → step/2 → step/3 → step/4 → step/5 → step/6/rppg/ → complete/
###  Each step is independent — submit in any order, re-submit to update.
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl      = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@contentType  = application/json
@accessToken  = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  GET current onboarding profile  (all steps combined)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  STEP 1 – Personal Info
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/step/1/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "full_name": "Sarah Johnson",
  "age": 28,
  "ethnicity": "white"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  STEP 2 – Physical Measurements  (BMI computed server-side)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/step/2/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "height_cm": 165,
  "weight_kg": 62
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  STEP 3 – Skin Changes  (Acanthosis Nigricans)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/step/3/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "has_skin_changes": false
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  STEP 4 – Menstrual History
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/step/4/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "cycle_length_days": 28,
  "periods_per_year": 12,
  "cycle_regularity": "regular"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  STEP 5 – Wearable Setup  (use "none" to skip)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/step/5/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "selected_wearable": "apple_watch"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  STEP 5 – Skip wearable
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/step/5/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "selected_wearable": "none"
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  STEP 6 – rPPG Baseline  (mark as captured after frontend capture)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/step/6/rppg/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "baseline_captured": true
}

### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
###  COMPLETE ONBOARDING  (call after all steps done)
### ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/complete/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
